Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志：\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正环绕Psi2000的轨道飞行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our position: Orbiting Psi 2000,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗古老的行星，现在已是冰冻荒地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}an ancient world, now a frozen wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,正分崩离析地走向灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about to rip apart in its death throes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.23,0:00:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的任务是接回在下面的一队科研小组\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our mission: Pick up a scientific party below,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,观测这颗行星毁灭的历程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}observe the disintegration of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 检查生命支持系统 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Check out the life-support systems. - Right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所有生命支持系统都被关闭了，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All life systems were off, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她是被勒死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone strangled this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.09,0:01:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 后面还有四个 - 死了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The other four are back there. - Dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的，长官 - 工程师在岗吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Right, sir. - Engineer at his post?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他就像是毫不在意的冻僵在那\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's frozen there like he didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哦…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,您最好自己去看一下，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Better look for yourself, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个人当时在淋浴，还穿戴整齐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One man was taking a shower fully clothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定要避免直接接触这里的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Be certain we expose ourselves to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克呼叫进取号，是否收到？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock here. Do you read, Enterprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是寇克，收到 - 全站人员死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk. Affirmative. - All station personnel are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么原因？ - 还不清楚，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- what caused it? - Unknown, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,像是我们从未遇到过的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's like nothing we've dealt with before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命与新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=THE LAST FANTASY=-\N荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：土豆爱 曼珠 kmdangdangli\N校对：心痕依，Micezhang，xjCGI{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,第一季第四集\N率真时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历1704.2\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 1704.2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,待接回的科学小组人员全部死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The science party we were to have picked up has been found dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,生命支持系统被关闭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Life-support systems had been turned off,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,全站人员冰冻至死，情况极其罕见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}station personnel frozen to death, conditions highly unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,同时，我们依然在环绕轨道上继续执行任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Meanwhile, we remain in orbit to complete our mission:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对行星毁灭的近距离科学观测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Close scientific measurement of the break-up of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你收到我刚才的通知了吗，史考特先生？ - 收到了，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Did you receive my signal, Mr. Scott? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,开始净化处理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Decontaminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这里是舰长 - 史波克和托莫伦已经返回，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain here. - Spock and Tormolen aboard, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在传送室对他们进行净化处理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're holding them in the chamber for decontamination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,最好让医疗队也给他们检查一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Better have Medicine look them over too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉史波克先生，10分钟后我去那见他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell Mr. Spock I’ll meet him there in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题，乔，起来到那边去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're fine, joe. Up and out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你的的脉搏242\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your pulse is 242.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,基本没有血压\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your blood pressure is practically nonexistent,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你把你血管里的绿色物质称为血液的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}assuming you call that green stuff in your veins blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这些读数对我来说太正常不过了，医生，谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The readings are perfectly normal for me, doctor. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于我的生理结构和你们不一样，我非常高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And as for my anatomy being different from yours, I am delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长 - 他们怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain. - How are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们很好，吉姆 - 相当糟糕，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- They're fine, jim. - Terrible, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很糟糕，他们坐在那里就好像什么都不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was terrible. They were just sitting like they didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不管发生了什么，他们都无所谓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever was happening, they didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我一直在想… - 你一直在想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I keep wondering... - You keep wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,人们是否真的应该到那里去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if man was meant to be out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直在思考，你一直在不停工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You keep wondering, and you keep signing on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有何推测，史波克先生，那里发生什么事了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any guesses, Mr. Spock? Any idea what happened down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能说，舰长，那里状况很怪异\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish I could say, captain. Circumstances were quite bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是录影带可能会给我们一些提示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}However, our record tapes may show us something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,6个死人，6个人死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Six dead. Six people dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你最好休息一下 - 是，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You better get some rest. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，准备好录影带，看看能否找到答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Set up those tapes, Mr. Spock. We'll see if the answers are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 实验结果报告，医生 - 谢谢，克莉丝汀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The lab status report, doctor. - Oh, thank you, Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,请放下一盘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Next tape, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 光谱分析带，先生 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Spectroanalysis tape, sir. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好像他们失去了理智，被下了药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Almost as though they were irrational, drugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:07:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有个工程师看起来对一切都毫不在意，一个女人被勒死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An engineer there, apparently oblivious to everything, a woman strangled,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一个组员手里拿着相位手枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a crewman with a phaser pistol in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他使用计算机房，就好像那里是一个娱乐场所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He'd used the computer room as if it were an amusement gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个着装整齐的人在淋浴时被冻死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And a fully clothed man frozen to death in a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,场面如果不是那么可怕，这会是相当有趣的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the image wasn't so ugly, it'd be laughable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 绅士们，还没有什么推测吗？ - 肯定不是药物中毒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Not even a theory, gentlemen? - Definitely not drugs or intoxication.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,对录影带的生化分析已经排除了这点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The bioanalysis on the tapes prove that conclusively.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是某种我们闻所未闻的空间癫狂症\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could be some form of space madness we've never heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但一定是有某种病因的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it would have to be caused by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的光谱仪显示并没有污染\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our spectro readings showed no contamination,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,并不存在异常元素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}no unusual elements present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说在三录仪里没有记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or at least none your tricorders could register.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,仪器是被设计来记录特定类型的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Instruments register only those things they're designed to register.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙里仍存在无限的未知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space still contains infinite unknowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,地球科学部需要对这个星球的解体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Earth science needs the closest possible measurement
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,进行尽可能的近距离观测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the break-up of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为此，进取号要在相当紧密的环绕轨道上运行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To do this, we need the Enterprise in a critically tight orbit. Question:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是，那些人遇到的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could what happened down there to those people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是否会给这艘星舰及其船员带来不寻常的危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}create any unusual danger to this vessel and crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会需要全舰的高效运作，舰长 那会是个很难掌控的轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will need top efficiency, captain. It'll be a tricky orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,当一个行星开始消亡，可能会带来剧烈的变化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When a planet begins to go, there may be drastic changes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如引力、质量、磁场等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in gravity, mass, magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们，开会的目的就是要根据你们的能力和经验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The purpose of a briefing, gentlemen, is to get me answers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为我找到答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}based on your abilities and experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在危险轨道上运行时，我们容不得任何意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In a critical orbit, there's no time for surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你们开始在舰桥穿戴整齐地淋浴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unless you people on the bridge start taking showers with your clothes on,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我的引擎能把我们带离任何险境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}my engines can pull us out of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在接到您的命令后半秒钟我们就能曲速脱离轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll be warping out of orbit within a half-second of getting your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥呼叫舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge to captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,扫描仪显示星球磁场突然偏移4度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scanners report sudden four-degree shift in planet magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,质量也发生了改变，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A change in mass also, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了，不寻常的快速转变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's beginning. Unusually rapid shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们马上赶到，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On our way, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我记住你的半秒钟了，史考特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll hold you to that half-second, Scotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,花剑，它是一把很细长的决斗用的剑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Foil. It's a rapier, a thin sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，那你用它干什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right. So, what do you do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思，“用它干什么？”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you mean, "What do you do with it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,自我防卫，蓄意伤害，烤羊肉串？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Self-defence, mayhem, shish kebab?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你试试吧 - 试什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You practice. - For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，乔伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hi, Joey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,上周他想让我对植物学产生兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Last week it was botany he was trying to get me interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该收集叶子、植物种籽等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was supposed to be collecting leaves, plant specimens...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你的态度不对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your attitude is all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,练习击剑能让你眼明手快，雄姿昂昂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fencing tones the muscle, sharpens the eye, improves the posture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你和他说说，乔伊，给他讲讲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You tell him, Joey. Explain to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，乔伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, joey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧？ - 离我远点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You feeling all right? - Get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你没我级别高，你也没有尖耳朵，所以别管我的闲事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't rank me, and you don't have pointed ears, so just get off my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他怎么了？ - 没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What's with him? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,注意：轮机室待命警戒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Attention: Engine room on standby alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,全体在岗人员到舰桥集合，通话完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All duty personnel to the bridge. Acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定没事吗，乔？我们要走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You sure you're all right now, Joe? We've gotta leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是伪君子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're all a bunch of hypocrites.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,用我们的鼻子嗅探和我们无关的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stick our noses into something that we've got no business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们到底在这里干什么？ - 放松，乔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What are we doing here anyway? - Take it easy, joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只会给我们自己带来痛苦和麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bring pain and trouble with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,把男人女人都留在冰冻的星球上直到他们死掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leave men and women stuck out on freezing planets until they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在太空里做什么？好处吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are we doing out here in space? Good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么好处？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在污染太空，毁掉太空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're polluting it, destroying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有权利到这里来，没有权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've got no business being out here, no business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放松，好吗？ - 冷静一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Take it easy now, would you? - Now calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果一个人要飞，他就要有翅膀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If a man was supposed to fly, he'd have wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他要在太空里呆着，他就不需要呼吸空气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If he was supposed to be out in space, he wouldn't need air to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就不需要生命支持系统来阻止被冻死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wouldn't need life-support systems to keep him from freezing to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 乔伊，把刀放下，好吗？ - 你完全失去理智了，乔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Hey, joey, put the knife down, huh? - You're all steamed up, joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不属于这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不是我们的地方，不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not ours, not ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,毁灭、观察…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Destroying and watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不属于这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不属于这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有6个人死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Six people died down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我应该活下去呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why do I deserve to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要干什么，乔？ - 嘿，乔伊，把刀放下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What are you doing, joe? - Hey, joey, put the knife down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别做傻事 - 放开，放开！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Don't be a fool. - Let go, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我拿着刀子 - 快放手！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Let me have the knife! - Please let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,乔伊，别做傻事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}joey, don't be a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,乔伊…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}joey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,乔伊，把刀给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}joey, give me the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急情况！娱乐室，39区！我们需要医疗队！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Emergency! Rec room, area 39! We need medics!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，补充：\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, supplemental:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的轨道，正在收紧，我们对效率的需求，是关键性的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our orbit, tightening. Our need for efficiency, critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但对我们来说未知的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But unknown to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,则是已经被带到舰上的罕见疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a totally new and unusual disease has been brought aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 相对引力在增加，先生 - 自动补偿，莱利先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Relative gravity increasing, sir. - Compensate, Mr. Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是，长官 - 磁场继续变化，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes, sir. - Magnetic field continuing to shift, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,星球质量继续缩水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Planet continuing to shrink in mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克先生？ - 所有扫描站正在监控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Spock? - All scanning stations manned,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所有记录器功能正常，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all recorders functioning, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在轨道稳定了，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Orbit steady now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,显然，这个星球萎缩的比预期要快很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Obviously, this planet is condensing more rapidly than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很有研究价值\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A valuable study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们或许能看到地球遥远的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We may be seeing Earth's distant future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在太阳熄灭前，这个星球很明显和你们的地球类似\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Before its sun went dark, this planet was remarkably similar to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰舵响应非常好，舰长 - 很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Helm answering nicely, captain. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯状态报告，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Communications status, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 托莫伦的记录？ - 精神病史档案，性格分析\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Tormolen's record? - Psychiatric file, personality quotients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他想要自杀？ - 是否是自愿值得怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Was he trying to kill himself? - It's doubtful he meant to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他很混乱，一直在折磨自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was confused, self-tortured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来不像是我认识的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doesn't sound like the man I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直都很不自信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His capacity for self-doubt has always been rather high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,让我奇怪的是，什么让他如此强烈地表现出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What puzzles me is what brought it to the surface with so much force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他的呼吸频率在下降，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His breathing rate is dropping, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,用呼吸器补偿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Compensate with the respirator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,准备缝合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand by to close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,正在缝合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了？ - 相对引力增加了，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What is it? - Relative gravity increase, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是那个星球抓着我们猛拉一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like the planet reached out and yanked at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,进行补偿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Compensate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,轨道稳定了，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Orbit steady now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能有点紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe a little nervous, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可能啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This shouldn't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这人应该好起来才对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This man should be getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定呼吸器功能完好？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You sure the respirator is functioning properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他就快死了呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, why is this man dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,皮下注射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hypo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's dead, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口并没那么严重啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The wounds were not that severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是麦考伊，寇克舰长请到医务室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is McCoy. Captain Kirk to Sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,乌乎拉，监视通讯状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uhura, monitor communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 告诉麦考伊我有空就过去 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Tell McCoy I'll be there when I can. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,星球的解体马上开始，舰长，萎缩速度在加快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Planet break-up is imminent, captain. Shrinking in size at an increasing rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,随着星球继续萎缩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As the planet continues to shrink in size,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它的表面离我们越来越远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}its surface moves away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要盘旋逼近从而保持同样的距离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forcing us to spiral down to maintain the same distance from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，我们必须时刻准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Exactly. We must be prepared to respond instantly
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,应付任何突发变化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to any sudden change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰桥呼叫轮机室 - 这里是史考特，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Engine room from bridge. - Scott here, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,坚守船舵，史考特，如果我们需要动力，就要尽快得到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tie into the helm, Scotty. If we should call for power, we'll want it fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题，先生，你会得到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No problem, sir. You'll have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,收缩率看起来稳定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rate of compaction seems constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就去看看好医生找我干什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I'll go see what the good doctor wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有任何变化通知我，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Keep me informed of any change, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真不知道是这星球的问题还是乔的问题…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't know if it's this planet or what happened with Joe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我像个新郎官似的出汗不止 - 是啊，我也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'm sweating like a bridegroom. - Yeah. Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，凯文，何不跟我去健身房呢，我的朋友？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, why don't you come down to the gym with me, Kevin, my lad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在？ - 有何不可？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Now? - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 适度锻炼一会儿可以缓解一下紧张 - 嘿，苏鲁，那——？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- A light workout will take the edge off. - Hey, Sulu, what about--?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，苏鲁，别犯傻了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, Sulu, don't be a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,肠壁的损伤重不至死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Intestinal damage wasn't that severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我抢救了那么长时间，他应该能活下来才对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got to him in plenty of time. That man should still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他的死只有一个原因，吉姆，那就是他不想活了，他放弃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only reason he died, jim, is he didn't wanna live. He gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那只是推测，不是事实 - 嗯，有可能的，这是可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- That's a supposition, not a fact. - Well, that may be. It may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前也有过对病人束手无策的时候，可不像这次似的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've lost patients before, but not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,乔不是那样的人，他是不可能放弃的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not joe's kind. That kind of man doesn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,巧合吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可能吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.18,0:17:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是他去过那星球的表面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean that joe was down on the planet's surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你想问我这是不是有关联？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you're gonna ask me if it's connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是想这么问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's exactly what I was gonna ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，他已经净化处理过了，也进行了医学检查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}jim, he was decontaminated, he's been medically checked,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所有我们知道的检查方式都已经做过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we've run every test we know for everything we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那还不够好 - 我们把所有可能的都检查了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- That's not good enough. - We're doing everything possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，我想要那些不可能也被检查出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones, I want the impossible checked out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,苏鲁先生怎么没在岗位上？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why isn't Mr. Sulu at this station?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,磁性拉力已经补偿，轨道稳定中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Magnetic pull compensated for. Orbit steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你来接手，兰德 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Take over here, Rand. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没回答我的问题，苏鲁在哪儿？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You haven't answered my question. Where is Mr. Sulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,莱利在旁，无须惊慌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have no fear, O'Riley's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一个爱尔兰人可值一万个—— - 你已被解除职务，莱利先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And one Irishman is worth 10,000-- - You're relieved, Mr. Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,乌乎拉上尉，你接手这个岗位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Uhura, take over this station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的，长官 - 我就喜欢这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes, sir. - Now that's what I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,女人也上阵，普选权就这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let the women work too. Universal suffrage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 莱利先生，请到医务室报告 - 医务室？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Report to Sickbay, Mr. Riley. - Sickbay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我正要去呢，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Exactly where I was heading, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,安全人员，莱利先生正向医务室去，请看着他到达\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security, Mr. Riley is headed for Sickbay. See to it he arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克船长请到舰桥来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,乔呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's Joe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呃—— - 他死了，是不是？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Well-- - He died, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,…你的双眼如此动人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...you have such lovely eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮的女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pretty lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他是你的朋友，对你肯定是个很大的打击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know he was a friend of yours. This must be a terrible shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道乔错在哪儿了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know what Joe's mistake was?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他的出身不是爱尔兰人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He wasn't born an Irishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,黎塞留，小心了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Richelieu, beware!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,站住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你休想逃走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No escape for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,想离开这片林子，要么血肉相抵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You either leave this bois bloodied
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要么让你的剑来饮我的血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or with my blood on your swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布伦特上尉，接替乌乎拉小姐 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Lieutenant Brent, relieve Miss Uhura. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有什么症状？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What were their symptoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,目前的阶段还没有出现暴力倾向，但有轻微的迷失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Non-violent at this stage. Slightly disoriented.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,莱利看起来对自己相当满意，他好像——\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Riley seemed rather pleased with himself, as if he were--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,失去理性了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Irrational.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,或者嗑药了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or drugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没错 - 接安全人员，乌乎拉上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Precisely. - Security, Lieutenant Uhura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的，长官 - 苏鲁和莱利，一旦找到立即禁闭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes, sir. - Sulu and Riley, locate and confine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我要每个接触过他们的船员都进行医学检查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want every crewman who comes in contact with them medically checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，二号甲板，第三走廊报告说有骚乱发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, level two, corridor three reports a disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.47,0:21:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,苏鲁拿着剑…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Sulu chasing crewmen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,…在追赶船员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...with a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 交给安全人员处理 - 有意思，规律出现了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Put security on it. - Fascinating. A pattern is developing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.07,0:22:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,先是托莫伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First Tormolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,潜藏的个性被逼着表现了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}hidden personality traits being forced to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是莱利，幻想自己是爱尔兰国王的后裔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then Riley, who fancies himself a descendant of Irish kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是苏鲁，认为自己是十八世纪的侠盗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now Sulu, who is at heart a swashbuckler out of your 18th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Psi2000星球现状如何？ - 引力正在增加\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Present condition of Psi 2000? - Gravity pull increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已移动了2%，按理应该稳定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've shifted two percent and should stabilize.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舵手，稳定位置 - 船舵不听使唤啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Helmsman, stabilize position. - Helm is not answering to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 曲速离开这里 - 引擎没有反应，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Warp us out of here. - No response from engines, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那就用脉冲动力，把我们推离这个轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Impulse power then. Blast us out of this orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.89,0:22:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,脉冲引擎也罢工了，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Impulse engines also dead, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,轮机室，我们需要动力！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engine room, we need power!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特，回答！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Scott, acknowledge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们失去了控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our controls are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,接管这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,黎塞留，你终于出现了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Richelieu, at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,苏鲁，把这个——\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sulu, put that--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把这东西放下！ - 为了荣誉，为了女王和法国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Put that thing away! - For honour, queen and France.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,苏鲁！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,苏鲁，把剑给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sulu, give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 苏鲁！ - 我会保护你的，美丽的小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Sulu! - I'll protect you, fair maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我不美也不要保护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.18,0:23:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,邪恶的黎塞留！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Foul Richelieu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时候很想你教教我这一手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like you to teach me that sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特，我们需要动力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scotty, we need power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.86,0:23:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,轮机室，回答！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engine room, acknowledge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.74,0:23:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在召唤我吗，长官？ - 你是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You rang, sir? - Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我是进取号星舰的舰长，凯文·托马斯·莱利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Captain Kevin Thomas Riley of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是谁？ - 我是寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And who is this? - This is Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.37,0:23:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,给我滚出轮机室，史考特轮机长在哪儿？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get out of the engine room. Where's Mr. Scott?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.25,0:23:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经解除了他的职务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I’ve relieved Mr. Scott of his duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,厨师们，现在注意了，你们的舰长在发话呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now, attention, cooks. This is your captain speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.30,0:24:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我要给所有船员双份冰激凌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would like double portions of ice cream for the entire crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.97,0:24:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白怎么做吧，嗯？ - 是的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Clear that too, will you? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,现在呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的舰长将演唱一首古代爱尔兰人的最爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}your captain will render an ancient Irish favourite.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.77,0:24:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,“我会再次带你回家”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll take you home again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.19,0:24:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，以我们现在的下降速度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain. At our present rate of descent,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.65,0:24:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,20分钟后将进入星球的大气层\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we have less than 20 minutes before we enter planet atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.07,0:24:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,然后烧成灰烬，我知道的，史波克！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And burn up. I know, Mr. Spock!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.99,0:24:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历1704.4：\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 1704.4:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰失去控制，正在向Psi2000星球盘旋下降\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ship out of control, spiralling down towards planet Psi 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.29,0:24:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在没有引擎动力和船舵控制的情况下 我们还有十九分钟活命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we have 19 minutes of life left without engine power or helm control.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.37,0:24:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 莱利怎么进去的？ - 他说你让我们到舰桥去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How did Riley get in there? - He said you wanted us on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.34,0:24:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他切断了船舵的控制和动力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's cut off helm and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.67,0:24:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他还关上了门，锁定了门的机械装置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He shut the door and locked off the mechanism.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.59,0:24:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不能接通辅助装置吗？ - 他通过主控面板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Can't you get to the auxiliary? - He's hooked everything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.97,0:24:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,把一切都锁定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}through the main panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.18,0:24:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,去我办公室把舱壁的设计图拿来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get up to my office and pull the plans for this bulkhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.97,0:25:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,开门的唯一方法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The only way to get that door open
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.77,0:25:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就是切断这些墙内的电路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is to cut through these wall circuits here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.48,0:25:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,“我看过他们的褪色和枯萎”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've watched them fade away and die
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.20,0:25:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 状况报告，各区的 - 船尾军官室发生打斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Status reports, all sections. - A fight in the aft wardroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.83,0:25:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,安全人员报告船员间的冲突在增加\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security reports incidents among the crewmen are increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.08,0:25:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,警戒级别提升至B2，封锁主要区域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go to alert Baker Two. Seal off main sections.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.33,0:25:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所有甲板，警戒级别提升至B2\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All decks, alert system B2.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.17,0:25:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,重复一遍，警戒级别提升至B2\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Repeat, go to alert condition Baker Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.88,0:25:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,封锁所有主要区域，待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seal off all main sections. Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.97,0:25:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,已封锁，不管那是什么病，但愿波及范围最小化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sealed off, if we can minimize the spread of whatever this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.39,0:25:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 继续警戒状态，上尉 - 我操作不了，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Continue the alert, lieutenant. - I can't, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.02,0:25:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他切断了警戒线路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's cut off the alert channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.56,0:25:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,乌乎拉上尉，你打断了我的歌唱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Uhura, you've interrupted my song.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.73,0:25:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾，但是今晚不能给你冰激凌了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, but there'll be no ice cream for you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.53,0:25:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 切断他 - 我没办法，长官，没有可行的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Cut him off. - I can't, sir. There's no way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.91,0:26:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,注意了，船员们，我是莱利舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Attention, crew. This is Captain Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.16,0:26:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚1900时在保龄球馆将会有一场正式舞会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There will be a formal dance in the bowling alley at 19:00 hours tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.62,0:26:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 待命吧 - 没办法，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Stand by. - No way, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.92,0:26:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他控制了主控面板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He controls the main power panels.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.42,0:26:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他在下面可以直接控制所有线路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He can override any channel from down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.59,0:26:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩十七分钟，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seventeen minutes left, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.43,0:26:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,医务室呼叫舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sickbay to bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.44,0:26:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你可以连接我到医务室吗？ - 我能听到你，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Can you tie me into the Sickbay? - I'm getting you, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.11,0:26:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,听着，你能让这鬼星舰保持平衡吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, can you keep this beast level?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.78,0:26:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我已使苏鲁镇定下来，我们即将为他做检测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got Sulu tranquilized, and we're running tests on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.65,0:26:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,目前为止，在他的血液里无任何异常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So far, there's nothing unusual in his bloodstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.95,0:26:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,身体机能看似正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Body functions seem normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.03,0:26:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,莱利才是眼下棘手的问题，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Riley's the immediate problem, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.24,0:26:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有什么办法，让他恢复理智？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is there any way, anything you can do to snap him out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.29,0:26:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,答案是否定的，除非我的这些检测能有进展\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Negative, until I can get a little further on these tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.79,0:26:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我是莱利舰长，船员们，我有一些补充命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Captain Riley. Crew, I have some additional orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.05,0:26:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,未来，所有的女船员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the future, all female crew members will wear their hair
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.34,0:27:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要披肩散发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}loosely about their shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.22,0:27:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但要限制你们化妆，女人们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And use restraint in putting on your makeup, women.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.52,0:27:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,女人看上去不该浓妆艳抹的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Women should not look made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.56,0:27:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,现在呢，船员们，作为补偿我要再唱一遍…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now, crew, I will render "Kathleen"...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.15,0:27:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,…“凯瑟琳”！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.15,0:27:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了，别再唱了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please, not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.28,0:27:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,“我会再次带你回家，凯瑟琳”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll take you home again, Kathleen
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.60,0:27:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,“我看过他们的褪色和枯萎”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've watched them fade away and die
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.32,0:28:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经在上面安好了跨接器，我给你信号前原地待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've set the jumpers up there. Stand by till I give you a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.36,0:28:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,“泪水模糊了你动人的眼睛”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And tears bedim your loving eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.16,0:28:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,“哦，我会带你回家，凯瑟琳”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I’ll take you home, Kathleen
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.62,0:28:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,轮机室呼叫舰桥，请试一下船舵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engineering to bridge. Try your helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.54,0:28:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你们应该有足够的动力保证星舰稳定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll have enough power to keep her stabilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.17,0:28:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,来，让我们研究一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here, let's have a look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.39,0:28:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩十六分钟，舰长，我们稳定下来了，但仍在盘旋下降\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sixteen minutes left, captain. We've stabilized, but spiralling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.69,0:28:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急信号，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Emergency signal, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.06,0:28:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,四号和五号甲板都打作一团了，陷入混乱中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Both decks four and five, fights and disorders.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.07,0:28:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我接医务室 - 我不能接通医务室的通话系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Get me Sickbay. - I have no intercom for Sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.90,0:28:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他在不断转换着线路 - 看看你能不能帮上麦考伊医生什么忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He keeps switching channels on me. - See if you can help Dr. McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.86,0:28:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,最好先去看看史考特，让他快一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Better check Scotty first, move him faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.74,0:28:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他必须穿透舱壁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's gotta get through that bulkhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.46,0:29:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,船员，去实验室报道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Crewman, report to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.89,0:29:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.31,0:29:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我想到舰桥去，这位船员不让我过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm trying to get to the bridge, and this crewman won't let me by.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.15,0:29:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 船员，站到一边 - 哦，好，是的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Crewman, stand aside. - Oh, well, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.07,0:29:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- “我会再次带你回家，贾宁” - 史波克！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I’ll take you home again, janeen - Spock!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.08,0:29:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长口信 - 告诉他我正在尽力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Message from the captain. - Tell him I'm doing my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.63,0:29:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果我切断了错误的电路—— - 我们还剩十四分钟了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- If I cut through the wrong circuits-- - We have 14 minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.80,0:29:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我们遭受全方位敌袭，也再快不了了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even if we were under full-scale attack, I couldn't move any faster,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.63,0:29:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不能保持一个安全系数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not and maintain a safety factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.26,0:29:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,以你现在进行的速度，计算显示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the rate you're proceeding, calculations show
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.39,0:29:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你将会比剩余时间多用一分半钟完成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that you'll take a minute and a half more than we have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.89,0:29:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你担负不起这个安全系数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't afford a safety factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.99,0:30:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,活体组织检查实验室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Biopsy Lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.04,0:30:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,活检室，我的报告呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Biopsy, where's my report?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.12,0:30:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,活检室，回答我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Biopsy, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.46,0:30:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哈里森，我的报告呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Harrison, where's my report?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.71,0:30:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要去趟实验室 - 长官？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'm going to the lab. - Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.67,0:30:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么事？ - 镇定剂正在失效\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes? - The tranquilizer's wearing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.59,0:30:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，好，我现在需要他清醒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, good. I'll need him conscious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.18,0:30:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,继续使用K1和k3程序检查他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Continue to examine him on circuits K1 and 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.68,0:30:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以了，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.60,0:31:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,把他弄出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.27,0:31:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我本可以早点过来的，但是船员穆迪——\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would've gotten here sooner, but Crewman Moody--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.32,0:31:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你来掌舵 - 长官？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Take the helm. - Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.48,0:31:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 掌舵！ - 遵命，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Take the helm! - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.07,0:31:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在呢再来一遍！ - 至少尝试切断他的声音好吧！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And now one more time! - At least try cutting him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.53,0:31:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，如果我能做到，你觉得我会——？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, if I could cut him off, don't you think I'd--?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.04,0:31:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- “我会再次带你回家，凯瑟琳” - 好吧，长官，我会再试的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I’ll take you home again, Kathleen - Yes, sir. I'll keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.75,0:31:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.92,0:31:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,“穿过那自然广阔的海洋”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Across the ocean wild and wide
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.72,0:31:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史考特？ - 轮机室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Scotty? - Engine room.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.30,0:31:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只剩下十二分钟了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've got 12 minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.55,0:31:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,重启引擎至少还得两到三分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll take at least two or three of them to get the engines up to power.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.43,0:31:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,顺利的话，还来得及，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then we'll make it, sir, if all goes right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.68,0:32:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,墙一钻通就叫我过来，完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Call me when you've cut through. I'll wanna be there. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.36,0:32:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,护士？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.61,0:32:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where is Dr. McCoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.86,0:32:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,去实验室了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's gone to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.95,0:32:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,实验室？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.87,0:32:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,实验室，请回答，我是史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lab, respond please. Spock here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.62,0:32:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,实验室？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.63,0:32:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克先生 - 有事吗，护士？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Spock. - What is it, nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.80,0:32:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.46,0:32:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯星上的男人对自己的女人都很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the men from Vulcan treat their women strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.97,0:32:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,至少，大家都这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At least, people say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.14,0:32:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但你有一半人类血统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you're part human too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.31,0:32:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不想…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.15,0:32:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.65,0:32:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,伤害我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.15,0:32:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.29,0:33:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱上了你，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm in love with you, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.84,0:33:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.01,0:33:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不论你是人类史波克…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the human Mr. Spock...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.85,0:33:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还是瓦肯人史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the Vulcan Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.85,0:33:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 护士，你不该… - 叫我克莉丝汀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Nurse, you shouldn't-- - Christine. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.61,0:33:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解你的处境，你是如此诚实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see things, how honest you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.78,0:33:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂你的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.28,0:33:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你外表冷酷，可内心却充满情感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You hide it, but you do have feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.24,0:33:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那些对你的冷嘲热讽一定让你很难受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, how we must hurt you, torture you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.04,0:33:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我能控制我的情感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm in control of my emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.46,0:33:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别人信，可我却不信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The others believe that. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.46,0:33:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.34,0:33:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不知为何，但我就是爱你，我真的爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know why, but I love you. I do love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.55,0:34:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就爱这样的你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.56,0:34:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,噢…我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.23,0:34:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.39,0:34:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长已前往轮机室，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain is en route Engineering, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.65,0:34:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你能接管舰桥吗？请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you take the bridge? Acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.82,0:34:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.11,0:34:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 叫我克莉丝汀 - 克莉丝汀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.87,0:34:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥呼叫医务室，史波克先生在吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge to Sickbay. Is Mr. Spock there?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.64,0:34:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, would you please acknowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.63,0:35:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,“我会带你回家，凯瑟琳”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will take you home, Kathleen
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.30,0:35:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就好，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Almost ready, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.60,0:35:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,“那里没有痛苦”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To where your heart will feel no pain
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.31,0:35:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,“待田野碧绿如玉”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the fields are fresh and green
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.15,0:35:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,“我就带你回家”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll take you to your home
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.78,0:35:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备就绪，长官 - 跟我冲进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Ready, sir. - Follow me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.83,0:35:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,相位枪调至击晕档\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put your phasers on stun.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.62,0:35:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,别轻易开火除非他有武器，行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't fire unless he's armed. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.50,0:35:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,“我会带…”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll take--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.46,0:35:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚没有舞会了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No dance tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.46,0:35:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,把他带走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.83,0:36:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,（简报室）
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.36,0:36:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我能控制我的情感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm in control of my emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.87,0:36:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,控制我的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Control of my...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.75,0:36:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我是名军官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am an officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.26,0:36:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,军官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.68,0:36:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我的职责…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.91,0:37:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的职责是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My duty is to...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.08,0:37:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,太迟了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.59,0:37:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.55,0:37:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,二【史波克用数偶数克制情感】\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.68,0:37:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,四\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.10,0:37:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,六\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.57,0:37:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,六乘…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Six times...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.95,0:37:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,六加三十…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Six and 30...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.00,0:37:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史考特，时间不多了 - 舰桥呼叫舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Scotty, we haven't got much time left. - Bridge to captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.13,0:38:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是寇克 - 已经进入行星大气层\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk here. - Entering planet's outer atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.47,0:38:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长 - 怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain. - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.97,0:38:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他把所有引擎都给关了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's turned the engines off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.18,0:38:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,完全冷却了，重新启动需要半小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Completely cold. It'll take 30 minutes to regenerate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.35,0:38:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰外壳开始变热，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ship's outer skin is beginning to heat, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.85,0:38:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,轨道测绘仪显示还剩八分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Orbit plot shows we have about eight minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.48,0:38:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史考特 - 我没法改变物理法则\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Scotty. - I can't change the laws of physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.15,0:38:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,必须给我半小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got to have 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.43,0:38:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，补充：\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, supplemental:
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.22,0:38:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号已失控，正在盘旋下坠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Enterprise, spiralling down, out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.77,0:38:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,与大气产生摩擦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ship's outer skin heating rapidly
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.60,0:38:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,致使外壳温度剧增\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}due to friction with planet atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.69,0:38:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我二十多分钟… - 史考特，只有六分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Maybe 22, 23 minutes-- - Scotty, we've got six.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.65,0:38:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,物质和反物质低温下不能混合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, you can't mix matter and antimatter cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.24,0:38:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,否则将会引发一次最大的爆炸，这将会是自…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'd go up in the biggest explosion since--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.99,0:38:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,均衡引擎动力便可使二者聚爆【聚爆可使引擎在低温下启动】\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can balance our engines into a controlled implosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.91,0:38:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,理论上可以，但从来没试过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's only a theory. It's never been done.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.58,0:39:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥，找到史波克了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge, have you found Mr. Spock yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.29,0:39:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,只有万分之一的成功率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you wanted to chance odds of 10,000-1 maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.42,0:39:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还要一个计算机组运算数周，才能得出公式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}assuming we had a row of computers working weeks on the right formula.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.80,0:39:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生不在舰桥，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock is not on the bridge, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.97,0:39:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才我还在舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.40,0:39:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿…大夫，我怎么会在这儿？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, doc, what am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.95,0:39:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊呼叫活检室，已经找到病因，开始准备血清\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy to Bio. We've isolated it. Start preparing serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.66,0:39:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是啥呀，医生？ - 是水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What, doctor? - It's water.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.12,0:39:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,行星上的水不知为何转变成了结构复杂的分子链\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On this planet, water's changed to a complex chain of molecules.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.20,0:39:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是啥，医生？ - 是被忽略的一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What's that, doctor? - That's how we missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.04,0:39:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,它通过汗液传染\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It passed through perspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.83,0:39:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦渗入血管，就会像酒精一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Once in the bloodstream, it acts like alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.00,0:39:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,降低判断力及自制力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Depresses the centres of judgment, self-control.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.38,0:39:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,派人去活检室！让大伙用血清治疗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now get someone to the lab! Tell them the serum works
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.67,0:39:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,准备更多血清！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and start preparing more!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.85,0:39:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大夫，让我走吧，我好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doc, will you let me out of here? I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.85,0:40:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,让他走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Release him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.56,0:40:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,轮机人员，各就各位，轮机室，报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engineers, man your stations. Engine rooms, report.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.60,0:40:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,循环室，报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cycling station, report.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.31,0:40:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,准备以应急方式重启引擎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This will be an emergency restart of engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.69,0:40:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你跑哪去了？我到处… - 我母亲…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Where have you been? I’ve been-- - My mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.86,0:40:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没对她说我爱她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could never tell her I loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.32,0:40:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就剩四分钟了，也许五分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've got four minutes, maybe five.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.87,0:40:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一位来自地球的女人却在一个鄙视爱和情感的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An Earth woman, living on a planet where love,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.20,0:40:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 星球上生活 - 我们必须冒一次满负荷启动的风险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- emotion is bad taste. - We've got to risk a full-power start.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.83,0:40:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,引擎被关闭了，没时间启动了，听见了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The engines were shut off. No time to regenerate them. Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.92,0:40:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只有冒险用满负荷启动 - 我尊敬我的父亲和那的风俗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We've got to risk a full-power start. - I respected my father, our customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.42,0:40:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的血统让我感到羞耻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was ashamed of my Earth blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.64,0:40:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}jim...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.06,0:40:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你我的友谊有时令我羞愧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I feel friendship for you, I'm ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.56,0:40:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,张大耳朵，听我说！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've got to hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.40,0:40:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要一个方程式！用聚爆这个险招\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need a formula! We've got to risk implosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.69,0:40:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没人试过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's never been done.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.45,0:40:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗，吉姆？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Understand, jim...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.99,0:41:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我一辈子都在隐藏自己的情感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I've spent a whole lifetime learning to hide my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.29,0:41:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只有聚爆才是唯一出路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've got to risk implosion. It's our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.09,0:41:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没人试过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's never been done.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.59,0:41:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不用你重复，科学官！只要有理论，便可能会实现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't tell me that again, science officer! It's a theory. It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.76,0:41:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能会变成一个最大的火球，规模不亚于太阳的爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We may go up into the biggest ball of fire since the last sun exploded,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.10,0:41:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此，都要抓住万分之一的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we've gotta take that 1 in 10,000 chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.18,0:41:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥呼叫舰长，轮机长想知道你是否找到…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge to captain. Engineer asked did you find--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.77,0:41:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,别再问史波克在哪了！我们正在说话！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I found Mr. Spock! I'm talking to Mr. Spock!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.27,0:41:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白了吗？ - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you understand? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.11,0:41:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还剩三分半钟，舰长 - 我被感染了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Three and a half minutes left, captain. - I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.61,0:41:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那种疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.78,0:41:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.83,0:41:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没有爱，你我都会好受些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're better off without it, and I'm better off without mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.87,0:41:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这艘星舰…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This vessel...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.96,0:41:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我倾之以心血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I give.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.00,0:41:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她不断索取\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.80,0:41:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她剥夺了我的生活，我和她已成为一体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She won't permit me my life. I've got to live hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.13,0:42:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}jim...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.64,0:42:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我有位美丽的文书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have a beautiful yeoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.14,0:42:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道她有多美吗，史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you noticed her, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.89,0:42:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以和她对视\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're allowed to notice her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.98,0:42:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长却不行…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The captain's not permitted...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.15,0:42:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}jim...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.32,0:42:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个混合的方程式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is an intermix formula.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.49,0:42:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于明白为何…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now I know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.99,0:42:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,它被称为“她”【船只第三人称英文用she】\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...it's called "she."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.99,0:42:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,公式从未经过验证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's never been tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.24,0:42:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,理论上提出了反物质与时间的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a theoretical relationship between time and antimatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.12,0:42:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她有血有肉，我本可张开双臂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A flesh woman to touch,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.34,0:42:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,拥抱她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.21,0:42:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以在海滩漫步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A beach to walk on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.80,0:42:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕就几天，让我放下肩负的重任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A few days, no braid on my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.18,0:42:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.18,0:42:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.02,0:42:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.19,0:42:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,准备混合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand by to intermix.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.94,0:42:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我会从舰桥调用这个方程式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll call the formula in from the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.94,0:42:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,已进入平流层，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Entering upper stratosphere, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.07,0:43:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,船壳温度高达2170度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Skin temperature now 2170 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.74,0:43:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须挺住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got to hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.03,0:43:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们，把走廊和涡轮电梯都清空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell them, clear the corridors, the turbo lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.00,0:43:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.85,0:43:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不放弃你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Never lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.23,0:43:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.62,0:43:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.72,0:43:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,【罪人，悔改吧】
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.84,0:44:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,轮机室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engine room.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.46,0:44:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're set.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.30,0:44:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,航线设为双曲式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hyperbolic course.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.89,0:44:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,方向，长官？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Direction, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.97,0:44:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,方向…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.81,0:44:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓，怎么来，就怎么走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It doesn't matter. The way we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.32,0:45:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,航线已设定，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Course laid in, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.57,0:45:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,燃料温度？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fuel temperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.82,0:45:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,接近零度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Level.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.17,0:45:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没沙滩可走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No beach to walk on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.76,0:45:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,长官？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.05,0:45:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,加热反物质，温度840度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Raise antimatter 840 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.93,0:45:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,需要四分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That'll take four minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.81,0:45:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间了，只有冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We haven't the time. We'll have to risk it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.89,0:45:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥，已准备就绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge, we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.57,0:45:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,启动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.25,0:46:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧，吉姆？ - 你呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Are you all right, Jim? - You?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.09,0:46:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,解药找到了，一切已恢复正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've found a cure. We're over that part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.89,0:46:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说，我们成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Obviously, we were successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.43,0:46:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 引擎聚爆成功 - 舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The engines imploded. - Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.85,0:46:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,速度计无显示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My velocity gauge is off the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.77,0:47:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,引擎能量也没有显示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engine power went off the scale as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.27,0:47:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,目前的速度已超出正常空间的飞行速度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're now travelling faster than is possible for normal space.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.57,0:47:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,检查飞行时间，苏鲁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Check elapsed time, Mr. Sulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.32,0:47:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,计时器正…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My chronometer is running...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.74,0:47:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,往后跑，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...backwards, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.66,0:47:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,【星历…舰上时间…】
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.58,0:47:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,时间曲跃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Time warp.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.46,0:47:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回到了过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're going backward in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.77,0:47:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,舵手，开始反转动力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helm, begin reversing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.19,0:47:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,慢些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.66,0:47:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,船舵正常，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helm answering, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.99,0:47:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,动力正在反转\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Power reversing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.59,0:48:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,时间恢复正常，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're back to normal time, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.18,0:48:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,前进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engines ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.18,0:48:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一级曲速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Warp one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.23,0:48:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一级曲速，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Warp one, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.35,0:48:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克先生 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Spock? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.23,0:48:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,时间曲跃…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The time warp...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.40,0:48:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对我们有何影响？ - 我们回到了七十一小时前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- ...what did it do to us? - We've regressed in time 71 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.28,0:48:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是三天前，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is now three days ago, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.62,0:48:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的三天还能重新再过一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have three days to live over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.75,0:48:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别再是过去的那三天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not those last three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.71,0:48:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这的确呈现出一个有趣的启示，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This does open some intriguing prospects, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.67,0:48:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,既然方程式有效\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Since the formula worked,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.47,0:49:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们便可以回到过去任意行星，任意年代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we can go back in time to any planet, any era.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.22,0:49:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天会用得着，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We may risk it someday, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.23,0:49:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,恢复航线，前往下个目的地，苏鲁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Resume course to our next destination, Mr. Sulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.90,0:49:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,航线已设定，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Course laid in, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.40,0:49:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,“她”继续稳健前行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Steady as she goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.07,0:49:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,本集结束
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.66,0:49:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-=The Last Fantasy=-\N谢谢观赏
